RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT a.collateral_code, a.collateral_desc FROM lbtms_collateral a WHERE a.record_stat ='O' AND a.auth_stat = 'A' AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM lbtms_tranche_collac_coll WHERE tranche_ref_no = ? AND effective_date = ? AND collateral_code = a.collateral_code)

SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO, B.USER_REF_NO, A.PRODUCT_CODE, A.COUNTERPARTY, B.FACILITY_NAME, A.CONTRACT_CCY, (SELECT CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER_NO = A.COUNTERPARTY) CUST_NAME, (SELECT PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_CODE = A.PRODUCT_CODE) PROD_DESC FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER B, OLTBS_CONTRACT A WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.LATEST_VERSION_NO = B.VERSION_NO AND A.PRODUCT_TYPE = 'C' AND A.AUTH_STATUS = 'A' AND A.BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND A.CONTRACT_STATUS NOT IN ('V', 'L') AND A.MODULE_CODE = 'LB' AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR WHERE PRODUCT_CODE = A.PRODUCT_CODE AND BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID)
